data.value: Hello, your computer has been compromised! All your files were encrypted and are no longer readable. Do not worry! We are able to restore your files in an instant, all you have to do is to follow the steps below: 1) Select a priority to decrypt (You can find an explanation about the priorities below*) 2) Transfer the specified amount of bitcoins to this address: 1N7PvCsFfEzCbG5nxjjhwj7MoAVa1ozTmH 3) Click "send decrypt request" button and wait for confirmation, then, you can check you request status. 4) Once your request is confirmed please click "Decrypt" button, please notice that the decryption proccess may take time. *Our algorithim has encrypted your files via priority, all your related work files and unrestorable files were given first priority, a second priority was given to your intimate and personal files , rest of the files that we found not important for you were given third priority.
